Zuora Z-Force Sample Code Package: Zuora Quotes Rules Engine Extension Sample Code

INTRODUCTION
------------

This Z-Force Sample Code Package provides a reference implementation of rules engine plugin capabilities. 

PRE-REQUISITES
-------------

This sample code package is an unmanaged package that depends on the following Z-Force managed packages: 
- Zuora for Salesforce Quotes Version 6.30

INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS
-------------------------

1. Install this sample code package using the following Force.com Installation URL: 

https://login.salesforce.com/packaging/installPackage.apexp?p0=04ti00000008o0p

This will install sample code unmanaged package into your Salesforce.com organization.

CONFIGURATION INSTRUCTIONS 
--------------------------

To enable the Rules Engine Plugin: 
1. On the Zuora Config tab, click Component Registration.
2. On the Component Registration page, click Edit next to the SelectProduct component.
3. In the Update component section, type RulesEngineSampleController in the Class Name field for the Quote Rules Engine Plugin type.
4. Optionally, give a description for the plugin in the Description field.
5. Click Update. Now the Product and Price Rules engine is enabled.

NOTE
--------------------------
To make the plugin work in UI, please change all the hard coded Rate Plan Ids in the RulesEngineSampleController to your own real data.
